BT /F2 15 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 704.89 Tm (1. Overall System Idea) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 685.89 Tm (The kiosk collects visitor feedback, optional pledge information, optional photo data, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 671.89 Tm (email details. After submission, the visitor earns a badge and a leaf. The same submission) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 657.89 Tm (can appear in three visitor-facing experiences: the feedback thank-you animation, the public) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 643.89 Tm (pulse screen, and the digital tree screen. Admins can control text, feature toggles,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 629.89 Tm (validation rules, page styling, backgrounds, badge leaf colours, and shared leaf size) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 615.89 Tm (through the parameter adjustment page.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 593.89 Tm (The central design choice is to keep editable values in one parameter configuration object.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 579.89 Tm (The backend serves that object through /api/parameters, while the admin page saves it) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 565.89 Tm (through /api/admin/parameters. Visitor screens read the same configuration, so the system) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 551.89 Tm (behaves consistently across feedback, pulse, and tree.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 521.89 Tm (2. Feedback Screen) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 502.89 Tm (- Quick Consent was removed from the visitor flow. Feedback is treated as long-term by) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 488.89 Tm (  default, so the visitor no longer chooses temporary versus long-term retention before) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 474.89 Tm (  entering the form.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 460.89 Tm (- The confirm submission page no longer presents Data Retention and Primary Consent in the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 446.89 Tm (  visible summary list. This reduces repeated consent wording and matches the long-term-only) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 432.89 Tm (  requirement.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 418.89 Tm (- The thank-you social buttons are controlled by the admin feature flag) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 404.89 Tm (  socialSharingEnabled. When the flag is false, the visitor does not see the social sharing) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 390.89 Tm (  buttons.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 376.89 Tm (- The thank-you and badge emails were merged into one response email. The merged email can) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 362.89 Tm (  include the thank-you message, badge result, visitor photo/passport content, and badge) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 348.89 Tm (  highlights instead of sending two separate emails.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 334.89 Tm (- The visitor passport is mapped by email. Each time a visitor completes feedback with the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 320.89 Tm (  same email address, the passport can show their own history and collected badges, giving) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 306.89 Tm (  repeat visitors a real passport-style record.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 292.89 Tm (- The feedback thank-you page now plays a flying leaf animation. The selected badge controls) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 278.89 Tm (  the leaf colour and target area, then the leaf visually joins the mini tree preview.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 48 256.89 Tm (Feedback Code Details) Tj ET
